      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.895 - Muawiya ibn Wahb asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about the practice of \"tathwib\" (additional announcements or calls made between the adhan and the iqamah).\nImam (as) replied: \"We do not recognize it”."
